</name></respStmt><item>Record created</item></change><change n="meta.33500"><date>01.10.2008</date><respStmt><name>HGV</name></respStmt><item>Record last modified</item></change><change n="meta.33500"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>IV/Vspc</date>
<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchite</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>θαυμάζω πῶς ἀκούσας ὡς <add place="supralinear">ὅτι</add> Τλήτης ναύτης ἐν τοῖς μέρεσι 

    <lb n="2"/>ὑμῶν ἐστιν καὶ <choice><corr>ἠμέλησας</corr><sic>ημελλησας</sic></choice> αὐτὸν συνλαβέσθαι <del rend="erasure">εσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>αι</del>· 

    <lb n="3"/>ὑποδεξάμενος γὰρ τὸν <choice><corr>γόμον</corr><sic>γομων</sic></choice> ἀπενεγκεῖν εἰς Βαβυλῶνα 

    <lb n="4"/>τὸ ἥμισυ σχεδὸν ανήλωσεν. βοήθησον οὖν εἴτε διὰ σοῦ 

    <lb n="5"/>εἴτε <subst><add place="inline">ἀξιώσει</add><del rend="corrected">αξιωσης</del></subst> <subst><add place="inline">τοῖς</add><del rend="corrected">τους</del></subst> <subst><add place="inline">διαφέρου<sic>ν</sic>σιν</add><del rend="corrected">διαφεροντας</del></subst> Μαξίμου ἢ Δόλιος αὐτὸν 

    <lb n="6"/>συνλαβέσθαι· <choice><corr>διακινεῖ</corr><sic>διακινι</sic></choice> γὰρ ἐν τοῖς μέρεσι <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>μῶν <choice><corr>δύνα<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ν</supplied>ται</corr><sic>δυναται</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="7"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ὲ <subst><add place="inline">οἱ</add><del rend="corrected">τοις</del></subst> <add place="supralinear">ἀπὸ</add> Ψαμμοῦρβ ἄγροικοι Δόλιος αὐτὸν συνλαβέσθαι. 

    <lb n="8"/><choice><corr>μεθυστὴς</corr><sic>μεθυσστοις</sic></choice> γάρ ἐστιν καὶ κακῆς προαιρέσεως. 

    <lb n="9"/><space dim="horizontal" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="10"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/> τὸν κακὸν ναύτην πάντα 

    <lb n="11"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">   λ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>βέσθαι αὐτὸν ἑπτακόσια <num value="700"/> διπλᾶ 

    <lb n="12"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> εἰς <choice><corr>Βαβυλῶνα</corr><sic>βαβυλωναν</sic></choice> καὶ τετρακόσια <num value="400"/> 

    <lb n="13"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="line"/> 
</ab></div><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1" rend="perpendicular"/> <gap desc="vestiges" extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="1"/>πάνυ ἐλυπήθην καὶ <choice><corr>λυπούμεθα</corr><sic>λοιπουμεθα</sic></choice> πάνυ σφόδρα διότι <del rend="erasure">τὸ κακὸν</del> 

    <lb n="2"/>ἐτόλμησας ποιήσῃς πρᾶγμα τοιοῦτο Ἀθηᾶτι <choice><corr>χριστιανὴ</corr><sic>χρηστιανη</sic></choice> οὖσα, διότι 

    <lb n="3"/>καὶ <choice><corr>λαικὴ</corr><sic>λα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>κη</sic></choice> οὖσα καὶ μηδέποτε εὑρέθη <supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ποιοῦσα</supplied> πράγματα τοῦ κόσμου. 

    <lb n="4" rend="perpendicular"/> <gap desc="vestiges" extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="4"/><choice><corr>γνῶθι</corr><sic>γνωστι</sic></choice> ὅτι σπεκουλάτωρα γέγονεν Θεόδωρος ὁ Τηείτης. 

    <lb n="5"/>ἦλθεν μετὰ Θέωνος τοῦ ἀδελφοῦ μου. 

    <lb n="6" rend="perpendicular"/> <gap desc="vestiges" extent="unknown" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> </ab></div></div><div n="meta.33500" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.33500" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="500" notBefore="301" type="textDate">IV - V</date></p></div><div n="meta.33500" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Textus prior: SB XVIII 14039.</p></div><div n="meta.33500" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Laur.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">42</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">33500</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0147</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">42</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0147;2;42" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.33500" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">164</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">92</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.33500" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Tav. XLII und XLII bis</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.33500" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Tibiletti, Lettere private 34</bibl></div><div n="meta.33500" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="it"><head lang="de">Italienisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Tibiletti, Lettere private (1979), 34</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.33500" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><geogName cert="high" type="nome">Oxyrhynchites</geogName>, <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>